    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine is strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, providing a dependable driving experience for its next owner. While the exterior and interior show some light signs of regular use, there are no major mechanical issues or significant cosmetic defects to report. It\u2019s a solid, reliable car that is ready for the road immediately.",
